mcp-server-webdriver (0.5.0-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Add 8 new tools for everyday browser use
  * browser_scroll: scroll page to coords, by offset, or element into
    view
  * browser_press_key: send enter/tab/escape/arrow/f-keys
  * browser_hover: mouse hover for :hover states and dropdown menus
  * browser_find_elements: enumerate all elements matching a CSS
    selector
  * browser_accept_dialog / browser_dismiss_dialog: JS
    alert/confirm/prompt
  * browser_get_cookies / browser_set_cookie: cookie inspection and
    injection
  * browser_open: URL is now optional (default about:blank)
  * browser_navigate / browser_open: auto-prepend https:// to bare
    hostnames
  * browser_execute_js: return JSON-serialised result instead of str()
  * browser_wait: add condition param
    (visible/clickable/present/text:<str>)
  * devtools_network_all: add limit= parameter to cap context-window
    size

 -- vitex <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Sun, 21 Jun 2026 17:11:24 +0200

